commit message: Move fling processing to Touch class. Add a small sleep in the draw loop
Add code folding. Also re-order code.
More refactor. Also fix cache thread. Now sleeps until needed.
Cache is suspended during a fling. Makes the fling less jumpy.

Fixed problem with small movements going to INITIALIZED when it
shouldn't
Lots of changes to make code easier to understand

Moved the last bits of tech from Scene to InputStreamScene. Now ready
for prime time.
Added ability to modify view after drawing it.
Fixed bug in scene -- DrawThread would never quit.
The map now saves its state for restarts from an oom condition.
Point does not like to be Parcelable for some reason.
minSdkVersion must be 10 because of the BitmapRegionDecoder api
new files for release to Google Play Store
